title: Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker: An Exploration in Identity – A Video Essay

media:group.media:title: Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker: An Exploration in Identity – A Video Essay
media:group.media:description:
A video brought to you by MooPer, showing that we are lucky to have experienced an incredible trilogy that forces us to ask "What if?" and answers that question with courage and insight not previously seen in the saga it's saving. 

I know people will disagree but i'm just right, Disney has elevated a broken franchise to Magnumi-Opusau (Latin for "Perfect good") And thanks to my extensive Filmic School Education, I can teach you why this film trilogy is better than you could ever understand.
